**Stalker** | Townsfolk Power
__Basics__
After Day 1, the Stalker may assign two extra invisible votes to a player in the current day’s lynch poll.
__Details__
After Day 1, the Stalker may threaten a player. That player will have two more invisible votes against them on the daily lynch poll. These additional votes are not revealed, instead the threatened player may win the lynch even if they dont have the most votes. The threatened player is not informed that they are threatened. Threatening a player is an end-day ability.

__Simplified__
After Day 1, the Stalker may assign two extra invisible votes to a player in the current day’s lynch poll.
